channel.title: The Pirates! Band Of Misfits
channel.desc: Set sail for a fun-filled voyage of hilarious antics with the biggest Band of Misfits on the seven seas! Pirate Captain sets out on a mission to defeat his rivals Black Bellamy and Cutlass Liz for the Pirate of the Year award and must never lose sight of what a pirate loves best: Adventure!
